<h2>Articles and Sections</h2>
<p style="margin-bottom:10px;">The <strong>w3-container</strong> class can be
    used to style &lt;article&gt; and &lt;section&gt; elements:</p>
<div class="w3-example">
    <h3>Example</h3>
    <div class="w3-code notranslate htmlHigh">
